OL,3,CNewcastle's Champions League journey
OL,4,Cended by stunning Barcelona display
OL,6,FBarcelona killed off Newcastle's
OL,7,FChampions League dream as they
OL,8,Fsurvived a first-half fright to book a
OL,9,Fquarter-final place in style.
OL,11,FA 7-2 win on the night ` a 13th on the
OL,12,Ftrot since their return to the Nou
OL,13,FCamp ` and an 8-3 aggregate victory on
OL,14,Fa night when Eddie Howe's side
OL,15,Fimploded.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
