OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773871878
OL,3,CNewcastle's Champions League journey
OL,4,Cended by stunning Barcelona display
OL,6,FAnthony Elanga's first-half brace had
OL,7,Fcancelled out Raphinha's early opener
OL,8,Fand Marc Bernal's free-header, but
OL,9,FLamine Yamal's stoppage-time penalty
OL,10,Fopened the floodgates with Fermin
OL,11,FLopez, Robert Lewandowski and Raphinha
OL,12,Fagain doing the damage.
OL,14,FNeither side will have been happy with
OL,15,Ftheir defensive display, but the five-
OL,16,Ftime winners eventually took a chaotic
OL,17,Fgame by the scruff of the neck to
OL,18,Fpunish a series of errors as the
OL,19,Fvisitors succumbed to largely self-
OL,20,Finflicted wounds.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773871878
OL,3,CNewcastle's Champions League journey
OL,4,Cended by stunning Barcelona display
OL,6,FHowe had plenty to be happy about in
OL,7,Fthe opening 45 minutes, but ultimately
OL,8,Fhis team, which last conceded seven at
OL,9,FArsenal in December 2012, head home
OL,10,Fwell beaten to begin preparations for
OL,11,FSunday's derby clash with Sunderland,
OL,12,Fa fixture for which midfielder Sandro
OL,13,FTonali is a major doubt.
OL,15,FNewcastle fell behind in calamitous
OL,16,Fcircumstances when, after Malick Thiaw
OL,17,Fhad slipped as he was turned by Yamal,
OL,18,FLewis Hall also lost his footing to
OL,19,Fallow Raphinha to play a one-two with
OL,20,FLopez before picking his spot.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773871878
OL,3,CNewcastle's Champions League journey
OL,4,Cended by stunning Barcelona display
OL,6,FThey were back on terms within seven
OL,7,Fminutes when Jacob Ramsey picked out
OL,8,FLewis Hall and he exchanged passes
OL,9,Fwith Harvey Barnes down the left
OL,10,Fbefore sending in a cross which Elanga
OL,11,Fslotted calmly past goalkeeper Joan
OL,12,FGarcia.
OL,14,FHowever, they contributed to their own
OL,15,Fdownfall once again within three
OL,16,Fminutes when central defender Gerard
OL,17,FMartin was left criminally unmarked at
OL,18,Fthe far post to head down Raphinha's
OL,19,Ffree-kick and Bernal controlled before
OL,20,Fbeating Aaron Ramsdale.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773871878
OL,3,CNewcastle's Champions League journey
OL,4,Cended by stunning Barcelona display
OL,6,FThe Magpies levelled again five
OL,7,Fminutes later when Yamal's ill-judged
OL,8,Fback-heel was picked off by Hall, who
OL,9,Ffed Barnes to cross for Elanga to
OL,10,Fslide home.
OL,12,FThey might have been ahead within
OL,13,Fseconds, only for Anthony Gordon to
OL,14,Fsteer Elanga's cross wide, but they
OL,15,Fwould have been behind had Dan Burn
OL,16,Fnot managed to block a Lewandowski
OL,17,Fshot after Thiaw had
OL,18,Funcharacteristically gifted possession
OL,19,Fto Raphinha, or had Yamal not blazed
OL,20,Fover after Ramsdale had saved
OL,21,FRaphinha's attempt.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773871878
OL,3,CNewcastle's Champions League journey
OL,4,Cended by stunning Barcelona display
OL,6,FBut they did succumb once again in the
OL,7,Fseventh minute of stoppage time when,
OL,8,Fafter French referee Francois Letexier
OL,9,Fhad been advised to review Kieran
OL,10,FTrippier's challenge on Raphinha as he
OL,11,Fattempted to convert Lopez's cross,
OL,12,FYamal stepped up to send the resulting
OL,13,Fpenalty past Ramsdale.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
