PN,42107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1773871878
OL,3,CNewcastle's Champions League journey
OL,4,Cended by stunning Barcelona display
OL,6,FRamsdale was beaten for the fourth
OL,7,Ftime seven minutes into the second
OL,8,Fhalf when Raphinha turned Martin's
OL,9,Fpass around the corner for Lopez to
OL,10,Frace through and side-foot
OL,11,Fnonchalantly into the bottom corner,
OL,12,Fand there was worse to come within
OL,13,Ffour minutes when Lewandowski powered
OL,14,Fhome a Raphinha corner.
OL,16,FThe Pole doubled his tally with an
OL,17,Femphatic 61st-minute finish after
OL,18,FYamal had bamboozled both Burn and
OL,19,FThiaw, and Raphinha rounded off the
OL,20,Fscoring after intercepting Ramsey's
OL,21,Fwoeful pass across his own goal.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
